    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="无规律的字母组合"><a href="#无规律的字母组合" class="headerlink" title="无规律的字母组合"></a>无规律的字母组合</h1><ul><li>必须得会读，会读才能拿分。</li></ul><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203131107992.png" alt="image-20220313110717857"></p><ul><li>break a leg ==good luck 祝你好运</li><li>leave me alone 让我单独呆一会。</li><li>I have no idea. 我不知道。</li><li>（1）记忆：打破大牛排。</li></ul><hr><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203131112812.png" alt="image-20220313111237681"></p><ul><li>（4）只有heart，找到直接选。</li></ul><hr><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203131119296.png" alt="image-20220313111928165"></p><ul><li>Don’t trouble trouble until trouble troubles you. 不要自寻烦恼。</li><li>be proud of  为…感到骄傲</li></ul><h2 id="补充："><a href="#补充：" class="headerlink" title="补充："></a>补充：</h2><p>（1）outside、proud</p><p>（2）couple、</p><hr><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203131120324.png" alt="image-20220313112041210"></p><hr><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203131123084.png" alt="image-20220313112337966"></p><hr><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203131125913.png" alt="image-20220313112509756"></p><hr><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203131126446.png" alt="image-20220313112636332"></p><hr><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203131128972.png" alt="image-20220313112820866"></p><hr><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203131236188.png" alt="image-20220313123156855"></p>]]></content>
    
    
