    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="二维数组"><a href="#二维数组" class="headerlink" title="二维数组"></a>二维数组</h1><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203061029388.png" alt="image-20220306102914237"></p><ul><li>一维数组和二维数组在内存中都是连续存放的</li></ul><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203061033207.png" alt="image-20220306103342033"></p><ul><li>未初始化int数组默认为0</li></ul><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/03/08/XdasMh85RYSN6P1.png" alt="image-20220306103537188"></p><ul><li>第一维长度数可以省略，第二位长度数永远不能省略。</li></ul><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203061042137.png" alt="image-20220306104208973"></p><ul><li>遇到\0即结束计算字符串长度，否则’\101’视为一个长度。 </li></ul><h1 id="函数"><a href="#函数" class="headerlink" title="函数"></a>函数</h1><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203061044825.png" alt="image-20220306104410648"></p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203061044358.png" alt="image-20220306104437220"></p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203061049783.png" alt="image-20220306104941663"></p><ul><li>全局变量未初始化值为0，内部变量未初始化值为随机数。</li></ul><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203061051242.png" alt="image-20220306105123128"></p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203061052791.png" alt="image-20220306105205609"></p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203061054253.png" alt="image-20220306105427079"></p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203061055339.png" alt="image-20220306105558176"></p><h1 id="值传递机制"><a href="#值传递机制" class="headerlink" title="值传递机制"></a>值传递机制</h1><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203061057771.png" alt="image-20220306105752580"></p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203061059605.png" alt="image-20220306105903403"></p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2022/03/08/r1VSGWKCaZQXMFE.png" alt=""></p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203061103382.png" alt="image-20220306110322264"></p>]]></content>
    
    
