    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="速率"><a href="#速率" class="headerlink" title="速率"></a>速率</h1><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203051509908.png" alt="image-20220305150923764"></p><h1 id="带宽"><a href="#带宽" class="headerlink" title="带宽"></a>带宽</h1><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203051514121.png" alt="image-20220305151414963"></p><ul><li>带宽大小不影响传输速率，只影响发送速率。</li></ul><h1 id="吞吐量"><a href="#吞吐量" class="headerlink" title="吞吐量"></a>吞吐量</h1><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203051518331.png" alt="image-20220305151819194"></p><h1 id="时延"><a href="#时延" class="headerlink" title="时延"></a>时延</h1><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203051524624.png" alt="image-20220305152411482"></p><h1 id="时延带宽积"><a href="#时延带宽积" class="headerlink" title="时延带宽积"></a>时延带宽积</h1><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203051526615.png" alt="image-20220305152612491"></p><h1 id="往返时延RTT"><a href="#往返时延RTT" class="headerlink" title="往返时延RTT"></a>往返时延RTT</h1><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203051528499.png" alt="image-20220305152820367"></p><ul><li><p>即CMD调出命令行然后ping 网址 后返回的时间的值。</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203051530460.png" alt="image-20220305153043405"></p></li></ul><h1 id="利用率"><a href="#利用率" class="headerlink" title="利用率"></a>利用率</h1><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203051533505.png" alt="image-20220305153330372"></p><h1 id="脑图时刻"><a href="#脑图时刻" class="headerlink" title="脑图时刻"></a>脑图时刻</h1><p><img src="https://gitee.com/halisi7/pic-goimage/raw/master/Typora/202203051534850.png" alt="image-20220305153415717"></p>]]></content>
    
    
